{"tid":1702793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國戰線] 所有喺香港嘅美國公民同我入嚟!! 遙距寄Postcard俾國會議員!","createTime":"2019-11-10T02:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T03:23:38.000Z","uid":224007,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb243bb40f753cf8ffff0b70210007de4e9b5dd","tid":1702793,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"各位，又係我哋HKHRDA Postcard團隊！林鄭政府之暴政，香港黑警之暴行，香港人已經無得再退 !! 我們一群居美香港人繼續積極推動美國國會儘快通過《香港人權及民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n自從十月初我們推出明信片游說計劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">在一個月內已在美國本土寄出超過6,800張明信片</span>。由於反應理想，我們現希望將HKHRDA Postcard campaign 推至身在香港的美國人。<br />\n<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》在十月十五日順利過了第一關，在美國眾議院通過，現在到了第二關參議院卻出現暗湧。面對中美貿易談判和中國反游說，我們亦轉打持久民意戰，務求令 Co-sponsor 數目與日俱增，在美國朝野的立法壓力只會有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們促請現居於香港的美國公民出一分力，如果你支持《香港人權及民主法案》，可在以下表格提供資料(<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/HKHRDApostcard-overseas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2FHKHRDApostcard-overseas&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=e2b8bf38\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/HKHRDApostcard-overseas</a>)，我們會按照你在美國的地址 , 代你寄 &rdquo;Vote YES H.R. 3289 and S. 1838 Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&rdquo; 明信片給你所屬州份的參議員。(註：只要是美國公民，未成年人士亦享有同等請願權，也可以出一分力為香港爭取求援！)<br />\n<br />\n如果想跟進我哋HKHRDA Postcard Campaign 的進展，可以follow:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Postcard.HKHRDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPostcard.HKHRDA%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=4a0d2ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Postcard.HKHRDA/</a>. <br />\n如果想贊助明信片游說計劃，可到此網頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://postcardhkhrda.wixsite.com/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostcardhkhrda.wixsite.com%2Fdonate&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=433f0e2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://postcardhkhrda.wixsite.com/donate</a>.<br />\n<br />\n附圖為截至11月4號已寄出明信片的分布圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KbtpOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KbtpOg.png&h=9f0121dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1: Front of Postcard (download the original file at the link below for printing, don&rsquo;t use this)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XQh2AO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XQh2AO.png&h=c8e7e870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjifPfS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjifPfS.png&h=ff7925ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2: Back of Postcard (download the original file at the link below for printing, don&rsquo;t use this)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bf9THD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bf9THD.png&h=e01ea481&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">pdf link:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=28c01535\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0dbc73b3b1ad2567a72dc21091139332f0cb58da","tid":1702793,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9aLU4H7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9aLU4H7.jpg&h=34815ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f27f4d96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br /